 that you're building.

00:00:37.840 --> 00:00:40.760
 And that server, 99% of the time,

00:00:40.760 --> 00:00:43.160
 doesn't have a clicky graphical user interface,

00:00:43.160 --> 00:00:46.320
 it has a command line interface, a textual interface,

00:00:46.320 --> 00:00:47.160
 where it gives you a prompt,

00:00:47.160 --> 00:00:48.360
 you type some stuff and you hit enter,

00:00:48.360 --> 00:00:50.440
 you type some more stuff and you hit enter.

