 So if you're like, where am I?

00:06:31.300 --> 00:06:33.520
 You can say, go to tilde slash,

00:06:33.520 --> 00:06:36.660
 and then you know what that folder name is.

00:06:36.660 --> 00:06:40.360
 Let's see, do I have any files here

00:06:40.360 --> 00:06:41.480
 I can remove?

